@startuml spring-security-mfa-bff
scale 0.8
title Spring Security 7 — BFF Login Flow with MFA\n(Framework Reference)

actor User
participant "web-gateway\n(Spring Cloud Gateway)" as WG
database "Redis\n(web-gateway)" as RWG
participant "oauth2-service\n(Spring Authorization Server)" as AS
database "DB\n(oauth2-service)" as DAS
database "Redis\n(oauth2-service)" as RAS
queue "Notification\n(OTT delivery)" as N

== Step 1 — User initiates login ==

note over User, RWG
  **Trigger A — User chủ động nhấn đăng nhập:**
    GET /oauth2/authorization/{registrationId}
    → Endpoint do Spring Security OAuth2 Client tự expose, không cần implement thủ công.
    → Không có saved_request vì không có protected resource bị chặn.

  **Trigger B — Truy cập protected resource khi không có session (hoặc session hết hạn):**
    GET /any-protected-endpoint
    → AuthenticationEntryPoint intercept, bắt đầu Authorization Code Flow.
    → saved_request được lưu để redirect về đúng URL sau khi login xong.

  Từ redirect đến oauth2-service trở đi: cả hai trigger xử lý giống nhau.
end note

User -> WG : GET /oauth2/authorization/{registrationId}\n  hoặc GET /protected-resource (no session)
activate WG
WG -> WG : Generate state (CSRF), nonce (replay),\ncode_verifier, code_challenge = SHA256(code_verifier)
WG -> RWG : SET spring:session:{wg-sid-1}\n  {state, nonce, code_verifier [, saved_request]}
WG --> User : 302 /oauth2/authorize\n  ?response_type=code&client_id=...&state=...\n  &code_challenge=...&code_challenge_method=S256\n+ Set-Cookie: SESSION={wg-sid-1} (httpOnly, Secure)
deactivate WG

note over RWG
  **web-gateway session state sau Step 1:**
  spring:session:{wg-sid-1} = {
    state, nonce, code_verifier,
    saved_request (Trigger B only)
  }
end note

== Step 2 — oauth2-service: nhận authorize request ==

User -> AS : GET /oauth2/authorize?response_type=code\n  &client_id=...&state=...&code_challenge=...
activate AS
AS -> AS : Không có auth session\n→ tạo mới
AS -> DAS : INSERT SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-1}\n  authorize_context = {\n    state, nonce, code_challenge,\n    code_challenge_method, client_id, redirect_uri\n  }
AS --> User : 200 Login Form\n+ Set-Cookie: SESSION={as-sid-1} (httpOnly, Secure)
deactivate AS

note over DAS
  **oauth2-service session state sau Step 2:**
  SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-1} = {
    authorize_context: {
      state, nonce, code_challenge,
      code_challenge_method, client_id, redirect_uri
    }
  }
  SecurityContext: anonymous (chưa authenticated)
end note

== Step 3 — First Factor: Password ==

User -> AS : POST /login {username, password}
activate AS
AS -> AS : UsernamePasswordAuthenticationFilter\n→ verify credential thành công
AS -> AS : **Session ROTATE** (session fixation protection)\n  copy authorize_context → session mới {as-sid-2}\n  SecurityContext ← Authentication {\n    principal: username,\n    authorities: [PASSWORD_AUTHORITY (issuedAt=now)]\n  }
AS -> DAS : DELETE SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-1}\nINSERT SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-2}\n  {\n    authorize_context,\n    SecurityContext { PASSWORD_AUTHORITY }\n  }
AS -> AS : MFA check: OTT_AUTHORITY còn thiếu\n→ chưa fully authenticated\n→ custom AuthenticationSuccessHandler kích hoạt
AS -> AS : OneTimeTokenService.generate(username)\n→ token = random string
AS -> RAS : SET ott:{token} = username\n  TTL = 5 min
AS -> N : GeneratedOneTimeTokenHandler\n→ gửi OTT đến user (email / SMS / push)
AS --> User : 302 /login/ott\n+ Set-Cookie: SESSION={as-sid-2} (httpOnly, rotated)
deactivate AS

note over DAS, RAS
  **State sau Step 3:**

  SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-2} = {
    authorize_context: { state, nonce, ... },
    SecurityContext: {
      principal: username,
      authorities: [PASSWORD_AUTHORITY]   ← chỉ 1 factor, chưa đủ
    }
  }
  Session {as-sid-1} đã bị xóa (session fixation protection).

  Redis (oauth2-service):
    ott:{token} = username   TTL = 5 min
end note

note over N
  OTT được generate **server-side tự động**
  ngay sau khi password verified —
  không cần user request /ott/generate.
  /ott/generate là endpoint cho
  passwordless (magic link) flow,
  không dùng trong MFA context.
end note

== Step 4 — Second Factor: OTT ==

User -> AS : POST /login/ott {token}
activate AS
AS -> AS : OneTimeTokenAuthenticationFilter
AS -> RAS : GETDEL ott:{token}    ← atomic: read + delete trong 1 command
RAS --> AS : username  (nil nếu expired hoặc đã dùng)

alt OTT hợp lệ
    AS -> AS : SecurityContext update:\n  add OTT_AUTHORITY (issuedAt=now)\n  → {PASSWORD_AUTHORITY, OTT_AUTHORITY}\n  → fully authenticated
    AS -> AS : **Session ROTATE lần 2** (SessionAuthenticationStrategy)\ncopy authorize_context → {as-sid-3}\nSecurityContext { PASSWORD_AUTHORITY, OTT_AUTHORITY }
    AS -> DAS : DELETE SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-2}\nINSERT SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-3}\n  { authorize_context, SecurityContext { 2 factors } }
    AS -> AS : Issue authorization_code
    AS -> DAS : INSERT OAuth2Authorization {\n  code, code_challenge, client_id,\n  redirect_uri, expiry (30–60s)\n}
    AS --> User : 302 {redirect_uri}?code=...&state=...\n+ Set-Cookie: SESSION={as-sid-3} (rotated)
else OTT không hợp lệ hoặc hết hạn
    AS --> User : 302 /login/ott?error
end
deactivate AS

note over DAS, RAS
  **State sau Step 4 (happy path):**

  SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-3} = {
    authorize_context: { state, nonce, ... },
    SecurityContext: {
      principal: username,
      authorities: [PASSWORD_AUTHORITY, OTT_AUTHORITY]   ← đủ 2 factors
    }
  }
  SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-2} đã bị xóa (session fixation protection lần 2)
  → attacker sniff được {as-sid-2} trong window giữa 2 factors không còn dùng được

  OAuth2Authorization = {
    code: ...,  expiry: now + 30-60s
    code_challenge, client_id, redirect_uri
  }   ← chưa có token, chờ exchange

  Redis (oauth2-service):
    ott:{token} đã bị xóa bởi GETDEL
    → không thể reuse dù còn trong TTL window
end note

== Step 5 — web-gateway: callback & token exchange ==

User -> WG : GET /login/oauth2/code/{registrationId}\n  ?code=...&state=...
activate WG
WG -> RWG : GET spring:session:{wg-sid-1}
RWG --> WG : {state, nonce, code_verifier [, saved_request]}
WG -> WG : Verify state → chống CSRF\nVerify nonce → chống replay attack
WG -> AS : POST /oauth2/token {\n  grant_type=authorization_code,\n  code, code_verifier,\n  client_id, client_secret, redirect_uri\n}
activate AS
AS -> AS : Verify client credentials\nVerify code: chưa expired, chưa dùng, đúng client\nPKCE: SHA256(code_verifier) == code_challenge
AS -> AS : Issue access_token (JWT)\n  issue id_token (OIDC JWT)\n  issue refresh_token (Opaque)
AS -> DAS : UPDATE OAuth2Authorization {\n  access_token, refresh_token, id_token\n}
AS --> WG : 200 { access_token, id_token, refresh_token }
deactivate AS

WG -> WG : Verify JWT signature (public key oauth2-service)\nVerify iss, aud\nVerify nonce — chống replay attack
WG -> WG : **Session ROTATE** (session fixation protection)\n  copy saved_request → session mới {wg-sid-2}
WG -> RWG : SET spring:session:{wg-sid-2} {\n  OAuth2AuthorizedClient {\n    access_token, refresh_token, id_token\n  },\n  SecurityContext { principal, authenticated=true }\n}
WG -> RWG : DEL spring:session:{wg-sid-1}
WG -> WG : Parse sid từ JWT claims
WG -> RWG : SET webgw:oauth:{sid} = {wg-sid-2}
WG --> User : 302 saved_request (hoặc defaultSuccessUrl)\n+ Set-Cookie: SESSION={wg-sid-2} (httpOnly, rotated)
deactivate WG

note over RWG
  **web-gateway Redis state sau Step 5:**

  spring:session:{wg-sid-2} = {
    OAuth2AuthorizedClient: {
      access_token (JWT),
      refresh_token (Opaque),
      id_token (JWT)
    },
    SecurityContext: { principal, authenticated=true }
  }
  spring:session:{wg-sid-1} đã bị xóa (session fixation protection).

  webgw:oauth:{sid} = {wg-sid-2}
  → dùng để tìm session khi cần logout/revoke theo sid

  DB (oauth2-service):
  OAuth2Authorization = {
    access_token, refresh_token, id_token   ← fully populated
  }
end note

== Silent Re-authentication ==

note over User, AS
  Kịch bản: web-gateway session {wg-sid-2} đã hết hạn hoặc bị xóa,
  nhưng oauth2-service auth session {as-sid-3} vẫn còn hiệu lực
  với SecurityContext { PASSWORD_AUTHORITY, OTT_AUTHORITY }.
end note

User -> WG : GET /protected-resource (no session)
activate WG
WG --> User : 302 /oauth2/authorize?... (Trigger B — Step 1)
deactivate WG

User -> AS : GET /oauth2/authorize?...
activate AS
AS -> AS : Auth session {as-sid-3} còn hiệu lực\nSecurityContext có đủ { PASSWORD_AUTHORITY, OTT_AUTHORITY }\nKiểm tra validDuration nếu được cấu hình
AS -> AS : Fully authenticated\n→ không hiện login form, không hiện OTT form\n→ lưu authorize_context mới vào session hiện tại\n→ issue authorization_code ngay
AS --> User : 302 {redirect_uri}?code=...&state=...
deactivate AS

note right of AS
  Silent re-auth KHÔNG hoạt động nếu:
  · Auth session {as-sid-3} đã expired
  · validDuration của PASSWORD_AUTHORITY hoặc
    OTT_AUTHORITY đã quá hạn
  → redirect về login form (Step 2)
end note

@enduml
